Summary: two balloon like objects way up in the sky
divs: Sighting Detailsdriving my car, saw a reflection in the sky. stopped to get a better look and noticed two balloon like objects. objects seemed much higher than a balloon should be, much higher than the airplane i witnessed. looked like a reflective surface. had to move on in traffic. that was the last i saw of it.
